SUMMARY:Schmigadoon!
DTSTART:20260514T230000Z
DTEND:20260515T013000Z
DTSTAMP:20260404T063851Z
UID:1825414
DESCRIPTION:<p>New York doctors Josh and Melissa set out on a couples&rsqu
 o\; backpacking retreat to rekindle the flame\, but instead find themselve
 s in Schmigadoon\, a magical town that&rsquo\;s a Golden Age musical come 
 to life. The townspeople won&rsquo\;t stop singing\, the bridge out leads 
 nowhere\, and the only way to escape is by finding true love&mdash\;which 
 may or may not be with each other.<br /><br />From <em>Saturday Night Live
 </em>&rsquo\;s Lorne Michaels and based on the Universal Television and Ap
 ple Original award-winning series\, this delightfully hilarious musical fe
 atures a book and Emmy Award&reg\;-winning score by Cinco Paul (<em>Despic
 able Me</em>\, <em>The Secret Life of Pets</em>).<br /><br /><em>Schmigado
 on!</em> is a love letter to Broadway&rsquo\;s Golden Age wrapped in a mod
 ern musical comedy that will leave you with a &ldquo\;song in your heart&r
 dquo\; (<em>The New York Times</em>)&hellip\;if you manage to get out.</p>
 
LOCATION:Nederlander Theatre\, 208 West 41st Street\, New York NY 10036
END:VEVENT
